This file describes how to install the PHPBind. 
PHPBind (class.bind8.php) allows for control of Bind 8.2's configuration files from within
PHP 4.0.x

REQUIREMENTS

1. PHP 4.0.x compiled with Sempahore and Shared memory support.


INSTALLATION

Copy class.bind8.php into a directory.  Add include() or require() in your php files with the path
of the class.
Edit class.bind8.php and change the location of named.conf and your domain db file locations.

